  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dungeon Deck is a cozy roguelike dungeon crawler, with a twist. The dungeon you are exploring is  a deck of cards!</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/88323633188865a28d807274dc52aa4e.poster.avif?t=1765448559\" width=738 height=341 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/88323633188865a28d807274dc52aa4e.webm?t=1765448559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find cool cards, create epic combos, and explore the dungeon!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choosing the right cards for your deck will massively impact your chances – only certain cards work well together! Visit the peaceful <strong>Meadows</strong>, a creepy <strong>Forest</strong>, or even an exotic <strong>Beach</strong>! Face fun critters and discover unique encounters! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/d9f27e3b0ab95baab5f99032792f07d4.poster.avif?t=1765448559\" width=738 height=341 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/d9f27e3b0ab95baab5f99032792f07d4.webm?t=1765448559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mix and match cards</strong> and discover combos that are unstoppable </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A uniquely tactile card game!</strong> Play with your cards and coins as they roll and slide around the table top</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face a variety of enemies</strong>, each with a unique challenge to beat  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A new deck every time!</strong> Face the unexpected with a randomly created deck of cards, and discover different items and events every time you play</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/7eb9356e1fed090d97ce0fdd37ab632a.avif?t=1765448559\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skillfully build your deck of cards with a variety of weapons and abilities: Wands, Clubs, Rings and more. Combine them in unique and satisfying ways to create combos and carve your way through a colourful collection of critters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >160+ unique cards each with different fun abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45+ colourful critters to battle against</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 exciting deck biomes with both harsh and cozy environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 powerful bosses - try to beat the boss of the <strong>Dungeon</strong> Deck!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 bonus challenge runs for the more skilled adventurers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/8d7851ba61d470988dbe2ee33d76bc13.poster.avif?t=1765448559\" width=738 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/8d7851ba61d470988dbe2ee33d76bc13.webm?t=1765448559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made with real love and care</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settle into the cozy tavern of Dungeon Deck as you enjoy the fantasy style soundtrack, and immerse yourself in the environments of each deck. Relax after a long day by facing off against quirky and charming enemies. <br><br><strong>Every purchase of Dungeon Deck goes directly towards supporting a hungry indie developer!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/f7956b08b9ec8be97146272bb8d304a7.poster.avif?t=1765448559\" width=564 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/f7956b08b9ec8be97146272bb8d304a7.webm?t=1765448559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895110/extras/f7956b08b9ec8be97146272bb8d304a7.mp4?t=1765448559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community and share your feedback - the developer visits every day!</p>",
